text.text: Control Kit by press WASD or the directional arrows.  Pressing W/Up makes Kit jump while press S/Down makes him crouch.

Welcome to Critter Quest!
  Your character's name is Kit.  Try moving through this level before the time runs out!
These are Gems and a 1-Up.  Collecting a 1-Up will grant you an extra life.  Collecting 100 Gems will also give you a extra life.
Kill enemies by jumping on their heads.
This is the exit.  Jump into it to unlock the next level.
Keep an eye open for secret areas!  Try jumping on the frog to get back up top.
